params.query:
SELECT uid, COUNT(*) AS session_count
FROM session 
WHERE created_at >= '2025-09-28 00:00:00.000' AND created_at < '2025-10-22 00:00:00.000' AND status = 1
GROUP BY uid
ORDER BY session_count DESC
LIMIT 50000
